Enhance collection update logic in cards.py for improved robustness and error handling
- Updated the collection update process to retrieve the latest user data before applying changes, ensuring accuracy. - Improved logging to provide detailed feedback on collection update results, including success and failure cases. - Changed the update method to set the entire collections field in one operation, enhancing efficiency and clarity.

Refactor create_multiplier_embed method in cards.py to improve embed creation logic
- Updated the create_multiplier_embed method to accept an optional user_id parameter, enhancing flexibility in embed generation. - Added a condition to ensure that the embed is only appended to the list if it is successfully created, improving error handling and clarity in the embed sending process.
